{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3ec73d8bb","title":"给马叙伦的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3f02f82a98","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"2b124fba19","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"马叙伦，字夷初，当时任中央人民政府教育部部长。"},{"id":"e62224c9b1","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华东局、青年团华东工委1951年1月11日关于学校工作给客地党委、团委并报中共中央、青年团中央的电报。其中第三项谈到，由于国民党长期反动统治的结果，学生体质弱，惠病者很多。但解放以来，各地未能很好注意“健康第一，学习第二”之原则，因此造成公立学校之体格最差，大学比中学又差的现象严重存在，这点应引起十分警。应按华东高教会议的规定，适当减少正课时间，照顾学生健康需要。毛泽东在这一段话旁边写了批注：“这是正确的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f473f5fd31","type":"title","text":"给马叙伦\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"},{"id":"2b124fba19","type":"paragraph","text":"夷初先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"},{"id":"e62224c9b1","type":"paragraph","text":"关于学生健康问题，前与先生谈过，此问题深值注意，提议采取行政步骤，具体地解决此问题。中共华东局一月十一日电报一件付上请察阅，其中第三项即谈到此问题，提出健康第一，学习第二的方针，我以为是正确的。请与各副部长同志商豹处理为盼！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"},{"id":"214c958748","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"},{"id":"fe8feaf4cc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"},{"id":"10f08c659e","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十五日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb"}],"page":{"id":"470ea19c40","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a3ec73d8bb","start":544,"end":544}}}},"__N_SSG":true}